'''奧蘭治兄弟會'''（Orange Order），正式名稱'''忠誠奧蘭治機構'''（Loyal Orange Institution），是一個國際[[新教|新教]]{{le|兄弟会 (宗教组织)|Fraternal order|兄弟會}}組織，主要在[[北愛爾蘭|北愛爾蘭]]活躍，此外在[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]、[[英聯邦|英聯邦]]、[[美國|美國]]、[[多哥共和國|多哥共和國]]也有活動<ref name="BenedettoMcKim2009">{{cite book|last1=Benedetto|first1=Robert|last2=McKim|first2=Donald K.|title=Historical Dictionary of the Reformed Churches|accessdate=17 June 2015|date=6 October 2009|publisher=Scarecrow Press|isbn=9780810870239|page=353|quote=Most of the organization's lodges are located in Northern Ireland, England, and Scotland, although others can be found throughout the British Commonwealth, including Canada, Australia, New Zealand and Africa. The lodges of every country are independent, but the Orange Order meets in a triennial world council.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.grandorangelodge.co.uk/what-is-the-orange-order#.UZO8UcqyEsw |accessdate=15 May 2013 |title=Welcome to the Grand Orange Lodge |publisher=Orange Order |quote=We are a Protestant fraternity with members throughout the world. Autonomous Grand Lodges are found in Scotland, England, the United States of America, West Africa, Canada, Australia and New Zealand. |archive-date=2014-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006071605/http://www.grandorangelodge.co.uk/what-is-the-orange-order#.UZO8UcqyEsw |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在政治上，奧蘭治兄弟會是一個[[保守派|保守派]]集團<ref>[http://www.grandorangelodge.co.uk/news.aspx?id=99829# Unionist Forum statement] {{Wayback|url=http://www.grandorangelodge.co.uk/news.aspx?id=99829 |date=20181116073727 }}. Grand Orange Lodge of Ireland. 9 January 2013. Retrieved 12 July 2014.</ref><ref>[http://www.grandorangelodge.co.uk/twelfthresolutions.aspx# Twelfth Resolutions 2013] {{Wayback|url=http://www.grandorangelodge.co.uk/twelfthresolutions.aspx |date=20141028164322 }}. Grand Orange Lodge of Ireland. Retrieved 12 July 2014.</ref>，支持{{le|英国联合主义|Unionism in the United Kingdom}}和[[阿爾斯特忠誠主義|阿爾斯特忠誠主義]]，在[[2014年苏格兰独立公投|2014年苏格兰独立公投]]中支持反对独立一方<ref name="bbc.co.uk">[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-scotland-scotland-politics-28020183 "Scottish independence: Orange Lodge registers to campaign for a 'No' vote"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-scotland-scotland-politics-28020183 |date=20201118113412 }}. BBC News. 25 June 2014. Retrieved 12 July 2014.</ref>。

